nodes.text: Darjeelai Swan was a Human female from Corellia who lived during the Yuuzhan Vong War. In 28 ABY, she joined Thrackan Sal-Solo on his journey to Yuuzhan'tar in order to have the Centerpoint Party and Corellia sign a peace accord with the Yuuzhan Vong. She was killed during an interrogation by the Yuuzhan Vong while Sal-Solo met with Supreme Overlord Shimrra.
